Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.58,0:00:04.38,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Even fate can be used\Nas a hint for reasoning...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.38,0:00:06.04,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Seeing through the\Nmost mysterious cases!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.04,0:00:08.38,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Genta's the lead actor today!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.38,0:00:10.17,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He might not be all that reliable as a friend,\Nbut we're all following him!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.17,0:00:11.72,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He sees the single truth\Nfor what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.72,0:00:13.59,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}and looks like a kid\Nbut has the mind of an adult!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.59,0:00:15.93,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}His name?\NDetective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.56,0:01:44.02,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Teitan Elementary School
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.65,0:01:44.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.90,0:01:48.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay, everybody, dig in!\NI don't want to see any picky eaters!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.78,0:01:50.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.61,0:01:52.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, geez.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.87,0:01:55.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A teenage boy eating\Nwith grade-school kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.45,0:01:57.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's so pathetic...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.35,0:02:00.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Personally,\NI'm enjoying the experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.92,0:02:04.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Growing up in the States, everybody\Nhelped themselves at the school cafeteria,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.50,0:02:06.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and I usually ended up\Neating alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.05,0:02:09.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's intriguing how Japanese schools\Nfoster a sense of community.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.51,0:02:14.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sure, this was fun\Nthe first time around...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.39,0:02:19.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Mitsuhiko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r},\Nyou left your carrots again!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.39,0:02:22.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uh, I'm just saving\Nthem for last!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.81,0:02:23.90,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.90,0:02:26.17,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}There's always somebody who picks out\Nthe vegetables he doesn't like.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.53,0:02:30.24,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}And there's always a dumb guy who brags\Nabout being the fastest eater in class.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.24,0:02:32.66,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Of course, in this class,\Nit's always...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.66,0:02:35.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hooray! I'm number one!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.74,0:02:37.95,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He beat Genta?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.29,0:02:44.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kobayashi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r},\NI'm not feeling too well.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.13,0:02:46.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can I go down\Nto the nurse's office?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.27,0:03:03.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's gotta be serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.33,0:03:06.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} left most\Nof his lunch!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.82,0:03:08.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe he's on a diet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.69,0:03:11.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way!\NYou know him and food!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.65,0:03:16.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}\Nhasn't played with us for a couple of days...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.03,0:03:19.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah. He's been going\Nstraight home after school.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.62,0:03:23.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe an upperclassman\Nis bullying him...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.22,0:03:27.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on! Genta's not the kind\Nof guy who'd get bullied.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.63,0:03:30.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And even if he was,\Nhe'd be safer sticking with us, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.51,0:03:33.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's a problem\Nwith his family.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.34,0:03:38.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe someone in\Nhis family is gravely ill,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.35,0:03:40.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,or his parents\Nare fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.32,0:03:45.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, we can't do anything\Nabout death or divorce.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.58,0:03:47.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,N-No...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.52,0:03:50.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's not it, children!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.48,0:03:51.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}S-Sensei{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.99,0:03:55.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His parents are fine!\NThey're still happily running their liquor store!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.86,0:03:59.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was worried, so I dropped by\NGenta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}'s house yesterday to check.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.74,0:04:03.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it sounds like Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}\Nis afraid of something.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.87,0:04:09.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His parents told me he was shivering\Ninside his futon the moment he got home...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.81,0:04:12.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is he scared of?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.77,0:04:16.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He wouldn't tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.47,0:04:18.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I kept getting, "It's nothing",\Nno matter how many times I asked.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.55,0:04:21.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But he might\Ntell his friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.43,0:04:25.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could you tell me\Nif he opens up to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.23,0:04:27.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Um... Sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.08,0:04:28.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bye-bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.32,0:04:31.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bye-bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.57,0:04:33.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bye-bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.75,0:04:45.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hold it, Genta!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.08,0:04:49.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you doing\Nbehind our backs?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.88,0:04:54.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you practicing\Nto become a ninja?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.88,0:04:58.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see! You skipped lunch\Nto slim down for ninjutsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.19,0:05:00.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah, that's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.43,0:05:03.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I saw this cool ninja flick\Nthe other day and...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.16,0:05:07.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then why were you shivering\Nunder the covers at home?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.81,0:05:12.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe you had a nightmare about\Nbeing attacked by a bloody samurai,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.52,0:05:15.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and you're training to\Nfight your imaginary enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.45,0:05:19.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It wasn't a nightmare!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.86,0:05:20.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I really did...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.41,0:05:22.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You did?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.12,0:05:26.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really what?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.04,0:05:30.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-I... The truth is...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.63,0:05:34.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,M-My life is in danger!\NA hitman's out to get me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.17,0:05:37.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-Hitman?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.93,0:05:40.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Knock it off, Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.76,0:05:44.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why would a hitman want\Nto kill an elementary school kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.32,0:05:47.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right... Unless it was me or you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.81,0:05:48.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.44,0:05:53.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I knew it was dumb\Nto tell you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.02,0:05:54.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.57,0:06:00.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r},\Ntell us the whole story!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.32,0:06:02.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I promise I won't laugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.95,0:06:08.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was walking through that\Ntunnel under the train tracks,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.12,0:06:09.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,when I heard these\Nfootsteps behind me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.08,0:06:13.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I couldn't see\Nanything in the dark,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.46,0:06:18.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but when I stopped, he'd stop,\Nand when I ran, he ran.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.88,0:06:25.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was probably just the echo of your\Nfootsteps against the tunnel wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.51,0:06:27.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's not all!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.27,0:06:29.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After that, somebody pushed me\Ndown the stairs on the overpass,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.64,0:06:32.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and yesterday a motorbike\Nran a red light and almost hit me...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.23,0:06:35.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was just coincidence!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.19,0:06:36.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was not!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.78,0:06:39.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And that guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.34,0:06:41.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.53,0:06:47.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A big bolt...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.95,0:06:49.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.87,0:06:51.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where could it\Nhave fallen from?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.25,0:06:54.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.80,0:07:05.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-It's from that\Ndepartment store sign.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.51,0:07:10.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The bolt just happened\Nto rust out, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.27,0:07:13.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're just having a bad day!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.31,0:07:16.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, maybe you should go to a shrine\Nand have them do a purifying ceremony...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.61,0:07:20.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No... This was more\Nthan just luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.03,0:07:22.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.11,0:07:24.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The cord on this neon sign\Nwas cut with a sharp object.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.49,0:07:30.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Someone deliberately cut it before\Nloosening the bolt, to drop the sign.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.58,0:07:35.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If that's true, maybe it was just a crazy guy\Nattacking anybody who passed by...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.92,0:07:39.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No. I think there\Nwas a specific target.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.26,0:07:41.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.01,0:07:45.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't this the Kamen Yaiba capsule machine\NGenta's always drooling over?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.39,0:07:49.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,T-Then he really is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.68,0:07:53.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Looks like Genta's life\Nreally {\i1}is{\i0} in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.52,0:07:56.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no doubt about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.73,0:08:03.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You'd better tell us\Neverything, Genta.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.57,0:08:06.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why are you a target?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.50,0:08:19.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You saw the serial snatcher?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.38,0:08:26.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The crook who's been snatching bags\Nfrom old people and unsuspecting women?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.14,0:08:34.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you tell the police?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.02,0:08:36.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah... About a week later.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.90,0:08:39.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I didn't see the wanted\Nposters until then.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.40,0:08:44.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They asked where I'd seen\Nthe guy on the posters,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.07,0:08:46.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and by that time I'd forgotten\Nwhere I saw the guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.16,0:08:52.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But then I saw a guy\Nwho saw the snatcher with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.62,0:08:54.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Saw him with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.58,0:08:57.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Five days ago, the snatcher\Nattacked a woman by my house,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.58,0:09:00.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and I dropped by\Nthe crime scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.88,0:09:03.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's when I saw\Nhim in the crowd...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.63,0:09:07.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The blond guy who was near me\Nwhen I saw the snatcher!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.22,0:09:10.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well? What did you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.22,0:09:15.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I grabbed him by the hand\Nand took him to the nearest cop!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.60,0:09:20.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But the guy said he didn't\Nremember me or the snatcher...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.73,0:09:23.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you sure\Nhe was the same guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.88,0:09:29.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah. When I saw the snatcher,\NI think that guy was sitting near me,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.03,0:09:31.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so he must've\Nseen the snatcher too...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.70,0:09:33.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You think?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.03,0:09:35.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I was really sleepy then...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.75,0:09:39.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I swear that\Nblond guy was nearby!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.58,0:09:41.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the snatcher?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.13,0:09:44.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think he was there too.\NOr maybe he wasn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.10,0:09:47.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A place where you'd get\Nsleepy after sitting down...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.30,0:09:48.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A movie theater...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.01,0:09:50.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Or inside a train...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.84,0:09:56.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,From the look of things, the blond guy is probably\Nworking with the person targeting Kojima{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.02,0:10:01.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez. Why didn't you tell\Nthe police you were in danger?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.06,0:10:04.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I... I got a phone call...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.36,0:10:11.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"If you say anything about me, you're dead!\NAnd your friends and family too!"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.95,0:10:16.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So that's why you didn't\Ntell anybody until now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.29,0:10:16.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.62,0:10:19.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is going\Nfrom bad to worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.21,0:10:23.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If he knows your phone number,\Nhe must know where you live.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.42,0:10:26.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah. If we went\Nto the police,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.55,0:10:29.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the snatcher might think\NGenta remembered something,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.38,0:10:31.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and there's no telling\Nwhat he'd do.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.39,0:10:35.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He might even be spying\Non us this very minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.27,0:10:39.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.43,0:10:43.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't you remember anything\Nthat might help us look for the snatcher?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.73,0:10:48.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I already told the cops,\Nbut he was smoking a cigarette with his left hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.99,0:10:51.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then the snatcher\Nis left-handed!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.86,0:10:55.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And he was wearing\Na weird T-shirt.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.12,0:10:57.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was black with\Na skull and numbers.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.70,0:11:02.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That one! That one!\NIt was just like that one!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.96,0:11:04.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.21,0:11:09.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you the snatcher\Nwho's after Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.17,0:11:09.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.92,0:11:11.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No. He doesn't look\Nlike the guy I saw.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.59,0:11:15.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who are you guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.01,0:11:20.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the snatcher's T-shirt\Ndidn't say "1999".
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.06,0:11:21.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It said "202"!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.74,0:11:25.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, do you remember\Nwhere you got that T-shirt?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.15,0:11:26.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.52,0:11:28.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A shop by the train station\Ncalled Bones.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.28,0:11:30.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.90,0:11:35.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's go check it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.95,0:11:44.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right!\NThe skull shirt is an original from our shop!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.04,0:11:46.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We've put out a lot of versions,\Nbut I don't remember one that said "202".
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.29,0:11:49.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What other versions are there?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.84,0:11:53.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"1999", "HELP", "ESCAPE"...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.13,0:11:55.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Lots of dangerous-sounding words.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.01,0:11:57.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You remember back in 1999,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.64,0:12:00.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,when everyone was talking about\Nend-of-the-millennium prophecies?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.22,0:12:02.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why we\Ndid a 1999 shirt!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.85,0:12:06.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you remember any suspicious-looking\Npeople buying those T-shirts?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.52,0:12:10.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dunno. It's been a long time,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.07,0:12:12.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and I don't really remember\Nall our customers' faces.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.03,0:12:16.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, that didn't go anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.74,0:12:21.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} could at least remember\Nwhere he saw the snatcher...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.41,0:12:26.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We could try movie theaters\Nand trains!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.25,0:12:29.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No. You can't smoke\Nin those places.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.75,0:12:31.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What about a restaurant?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.92,0:12:36.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's it! You must've gotten sleepy\Nfrom eating too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.34,0:12:38.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But that guy\Nwasn't eating anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.60,0:12:41.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was watching him\Nthe whole time,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.79,0:12:44.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and I just remember him reading\Na newspaper and smoking a cigarette...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.31,0:12:50.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How come you can remember all that,\Nbut not where you were?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.27,0:12:51.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Beats me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.03,0:12:53.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But that's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.40,0:12:57.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Didn't he get annoyed at you\Nfor staring at him for so long?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.37,0:13:00.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did he?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.53,0:13:02.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, our eyes never met...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.16,0:13:05.41,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.41,0:13:06.58,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}So that's where they were...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.54,0:13:09.64,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The skull T-shirt\Nwith the number 202...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.42,0:13:11.60,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The left hand...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.63,0:13:14.88,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}And a place where your eyes\Nwould never meet,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.88,0:13:16.59,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}and you wouldn't attract attention\Nfor staring at someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.55,0:13:19.72,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I've got it, Genta.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.72,0:13:22.51,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The very place\Nyou saw the snatcher!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.21,0:13:29.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Genta...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.42,0:13:32.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The optician's, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.05,0:13:32.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.05,0:13:35.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's where you\Nsaw the snatcher!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.98,0:13:39.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You said he didn't get upset\Neven though you were staring at him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.97,0:13:41.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Um, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.14,0:13:47.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He didn't see you staring at him...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.23,0:13:51.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,because he'd taken his glasses off\Nto have them fixed!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.73,0:13:53.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,B-But, Conan...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.48,0:13:56.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've never been\Nto an optician's.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.61,0:13:58.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, that's got to be it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.66,0:13:59.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After all,\Nit'd also have...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.67,0:14:08.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.38,0:14:11.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You've got it all wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.54,0:14:15.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? Seriously?\NI thought I'd cracked it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.01,0:14:18.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And you call yourself\Nthe modern-day Holmes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.05,0:14:23.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, now.\NEven a genius makes mistakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.79,0:14:25.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't feel down!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.96,0:14:27.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.79,0:14:31.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Call me if you remember anything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.00,0:14:31.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.96,0:14:39.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But where could it be?\NThe place Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} saw the snatcher?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.26,0:14:43.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A place where you can stare at somebody\Nwithout getting in trouble, and also get sleepy...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.72,0:14:48.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's school!\NGenta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} always falls asleep there!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.98,0:14:52.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If the snatcher was at our school,\Nwe'd have seen him too!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.86,0:14:53.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.48,0:14:56.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! Hold on a sec!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.41,0:15:00.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, for crying out loud.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.71,0:15:03.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You never stop eating!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.16,0:15:05.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're going to put on weight again!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.16,0:15:07.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who cares?\NI like to snack!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.79,0:15:11.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You got ice cream on your face,\NGenta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.67,0:15:17.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.13,0:15:19.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you remember something?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.13,0:15:20.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,N-No, forget it...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.43,0:15:23.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Be careful on your way home!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.89,0:15:24.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Later!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.39,0:15:29.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Three chicken and four liver, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.85,0:15:30.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Coming right up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.81,0:15:33.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm getting hungry...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.52,0:15:35.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Didn't you just have\Nsome ice cream?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.62,0:15:44.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,French food!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.99,0:15:48.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Show some self-control!\NYou're almost home!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.72,0:15:55.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Red... White... Blue...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.46,0:15:58.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?\NThat's the French flag.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.80,0:16:00.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Ayumi...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.09,0:16:03.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Have you seen the colors\Nred, white and blue anywhere else?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.47,0:16:04.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.64,0:16:10.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}'s always wearing a red bowtie,\Nwhite shirt and blue jacket...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.56,0:16:13.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-Is he the snatcher?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.85,0:16:18.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, right.\NWould Conan do something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.23,0:16:23.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't know why, but the colors\Nred, white and blue keep spinning in my head...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.95,0:16:27.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bye, Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.99,0:16:30.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't forget\Nto go straight home!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.08,0:16:30.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.79,0:16:34.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you get any fatter,\Neven the piggies will laugh at you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.38,0:16:35.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.21,0:16:40.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.01,0:16:43.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stupid Ayumi,\Ncalling me fat.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.18,0:16:46.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm not that fat, am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.35,0:16:51.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I remember!\NIt was back there!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.18,0:16:56.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The seventh floor of\Nthe building above the station...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.94,0:16:59.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The elevator...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.07,0:17:04.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, stop! Hold that elevator!\NWait for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.49,0:17:07.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which floor, little boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.58,0:17:10.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The s-seventh floor...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.91,0:17:15.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, kid...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.04,0:17:16.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-You're that blond... guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.50,0:17:20.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry about forgetting you before.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.92,0:17:25.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I remembered where it was!\NWhere you and me saw the snatcher!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.22,0:17:29.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Keep it down!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.14,0:17:32.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He could be\Nlistening in on us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.14,0:17:34.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then you remember too?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.60,0:17:37.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I just remembered.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.23,0:17:39.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's talk it over\Nbefore we go to the cops,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.23,0:17:42.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and make sure we've got\Nour stories straight.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.49,0:17:46.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Somewhere safe\Nfrom other people...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.78,0:17:48.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Like a restroom...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.37,0:17:50.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sure of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.83,0:17:53.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-It's him!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.70,0:17:54.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.75,0:17:58.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-I think the name he wrote\Nin our schedule book was Someda...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.96,0:18:01.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? Who the hell are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.55,0:18:03.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you don't knock off\Nthe accusations, I'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.09,0:18:07.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Left-handed...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.34,0:18:10.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A T-shirt with a skull\Nand the number 202...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.10,0:18:15.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No wonder the police couldn't\Npin down the snatcher's identity.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.14,0:18:19.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Genta was looking at your\Nreflection in a mirror!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.36,0:18:22.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-You're the kids from before!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.98,0:18:24.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.36,0:18:27.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And you never got angry at Kojima{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}\Nfor staring at you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.57,0:18:29.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,because he was watching you\Nin the mirror.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.16,0:18:32.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The "202" he saw written\Non your T-shirt...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.33,0:18:34.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,was actually "SOS"!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.70,0:18:37.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the left hand\Nwas really your right hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.50,0:18:41.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A place where Genta would go that has\Na mirror in front of the customers,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.84,0:18:44.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and where he could get sleepy...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.71,0:18:47.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was the barber shop, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.34,0:18:54.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Genta didn't realize you and\Nthe snatcher were the same person
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.68,0:18:58.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,because you had your hair\Nbleached while he was napping.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.52,0:19:02.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A guy with a black hair and glasses\Nchanged into a blond guy without glasses,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.69,0:19:07.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and Genta didn't see your clothes\Nbecause they were covered with a smock.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.24,0:19:09.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He misremembered you\Nas two different people.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.45,0:19:13.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What're you talking about,\Nyou little brat?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.16,0:19:14.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You've got no proof.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.87,0:19:17.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's an eyewitness\Nstanding right behind you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.62,0:19:22.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The barber who\Ndyed your hair!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.46,0:19:28.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You've been lucky until now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.72,0:19:31.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As it happens,\Nthe barber doesn't watch TV,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.80,0:19:35.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and the police haven't posted\Nyour picture in his neighborhood yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.68,0:19:40.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You dyed your hair black with coloring\Nthat could be washed out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.39,0:19:43.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I bet you thought\Nno one would recognize you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.31,0:19:49.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But the police got the snatcher's fingerprints\Noff the last bag he tried to snatch.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.07,0:19:54.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If those prints match yours,\Nyou can't talk your way out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.08,0:20:00.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,S-So what was this kid\Ndoing back in this neighborhood?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.29,0:20:02.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Luring you here,\Nthat's what!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.75,0:20:07.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We had him get ice cream on his face\Nthat looked like shaving cream...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.80,0:20:11.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and stare at the French flag, which is\Nred, white and blue like a barber pole!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.47,0:20:15.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then he stared\Nat his reflection...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.80,0:20:19.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,like he was looking\Nin a barber's mirror!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.73,0:20:23.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We knew all along\Nthat you were following us,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.65,0:20:26.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so we convinced Kojima{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}\Nto play dumb—no difficult task—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.57,0:20:28.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and lure you into a trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.74,0:20:35.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You kids think\Nyou can mess with me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.83,0:20:38.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-What're you doing,\Nyou old broad?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.70,0:20:41.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're pretty dumb, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.46,0:20:45.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You really think I'd walk all over town\Njust to lure you here alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.63,0:20:46.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.13,0:20:49.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right...\NLook around you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.84,0:20:52.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,While Genta bought us some time,\Nwe made a phone call.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.38,0:20:55.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This place is\Nswarming with cops!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.93,0:21:02.85,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That's how the\Nsnatcher got arrested,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.85,0:21:04.85,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}and the case closed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.52,0:21:09.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I couldn't believe the words\Ncoming out of your mouth!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.98,0:21:11.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you really a grade-schooler,\NConan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.90,0:21:14.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-It was nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.15,0:21:15.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just imitating\Nthe detectives on TV!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.87,0:21:17.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.38,0:22:54.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A huge victory for the Detective Boys!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.05,0:22:55.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hooray!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.34,0:22:57.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But you're so lazy, Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.42,0:23:01.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't believe you totally fell asleep\Nwhile the snatcher was having his hair dyed!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.18,0:23:06.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The barber said he didn't wake me up\Nbecause I looked so peaceful.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.89,0:23:09.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess they say sleep\Nis good for growing kids...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.40,0:23:15.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm glad you were right\Nand the criminal wasn't really left-handed.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.57,0:23:20.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I was pretty sure it wasn't {\i1}him{\i0},\Nsince he'd target me before Kojima{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r},
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.99,0:23:22.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but it did shake me...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.24,0:23:25.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, you don't mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.20,0:23:29.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You don't know?\NThen here's another factoid for your files.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.04,0:23:32.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Gin is left-handed.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.06,0:23:47.61,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.10,0:23:52.48,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}T-This is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.50,0:24:01.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sure he wanted to see\Nwhat was inside this attaché case.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.28,0:24:05.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See, the key\Nis still in the hole.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.19,0:24:07.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a curse.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.98,0:24:15.03,Signs,,0,0,0,,Next Conan:\NThe Fake Kogoro Mouri\N(Part 1)
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.03,0:24:20.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next Conan's Hint: Cellular phone
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.06,0:24:21.26,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Next time...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.26,0:24:24.22,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,How could the great Kogoro Mouri—
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.22,0:24:25.07,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
